## Overview

Implement comprehensive Arrow to DuckDB type conversion covering all common Arrow types. This is critical for the table function to handle arbitrary schemas returned by VGI workers.

## Current State

The existing table scan code in vgi_table_scan.cpp only handles VARCHAR:

```cpp
